 if you want to just learn a style, i think manga's a good choice(HTDM books are good) its close to real, but not close enough to be real.  Just remember that its your choice for style and dont be swayed by the majority if your heart says something else. <p>------------------<br>
<br>
art is not a hobby its a lifestyle you either love it or hate it, witch end are you on?<br>
